{"tid":601094,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"決意離開連登 這是我在這裡出的最後一個post","createTime":"2018-03-22T02:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T13:14:38.000Z","uid":14719,"like":9,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bd185970742f6668f2b82f0760fc0c85abd0a9d7","tid":601094,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:40:35.000Z","msg":"這裏的人學識都很高 <br />\n<br />\n從這裏的人的留言中學會了很多知識 <br />\n<br />\n天文、地理、氣象、歷史、政治 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這是我一上網就立刻到這裏的原因 <br />\n<br />\n正正是因為我自己都是一個愛好知識的人 <br />\n<br />\n加上這裏的人都多廿𡃁歲的，同我相若，啱傾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我在這裡出了很多很多post，但99%都是所謂的 &quot;假膠post&quot;，即是完完全全亂up老作搏大家一笑，<br />\n<br />\n帖內的內容和自己的事完全沒關，無論出post同reply都係，甚至好多時同真實嘅自己係相反 <br />\n<br />\n明明是阿仙奴球迷，卻經常出post揶揄阿仙奴<br />\n<br />\n明明自己都係工程界人士，卻經常出post話工程界一文不值 <br />\n<br />\n明明自己極討厭某個死卡通角色，就出post話自己愛上咗佢 <br />\n<br />\n歸根究抵都係純粹因為返學時無聊，所以無無聊聊地出個post <br />\n<br />\n講無聊野 <br />\n<br />\n然後一邊返學，一邊睇回覆，自娛一下 <br />\n<br />\n這件事對不喜歡現在的學業的我十分重要 <br />\n<br />\n同時，我故意講相反嘢，因為驚俾人知我嘅真正身份 <br />\n<br />\n一個知...就會話俾另一個知，然後一傳十，十傳百, 就不好了，我完全唔想俾人知我喺網上嘅身份，講過啲乜 <br />\n<br />\n俾人知道，我喺呢度暢所欲言，說傻話，減減壓的空間就完全被破壞了... <br />\n(雖然我出嘅post都同自己做過嘅野無關) <br />\n<br />\n不過，有一日我忽然發現自己沉迷了這裡....荒廢正業 <br />\n<br />\n離開，因為不想再在這裏浪費時間了，往後我還有很多計劃：操番好體能、籌備上雪山、練番水、練好啲壁球、鋼琴要考演奏級、練好渣車、重投放下了一年多的義工活動、抽多啲時間陪女朋友,、考番CFA (讀好左level 1 又因病冇考)...etc etc <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再見了，連登各位高學識嘅人。"},{"pid":"edf75798b7b15c1c918faa5a2d783b46e1632313","tid":601094,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:43:56.000Z","msg":"死五毛躝啦"},{"pid":"50cd7c9f01ed33b802a174b6a229b19dda9b090e","tid":601094,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edf75798b7b15c1c918faa5a2d783b46e1632313","tid":601094,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:43:56.000Z","msg":"死五毛躝啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:03:19.000Z","msg":"又屈毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44bdfca1d33796e5727caba63a757465624c2e22","tid":601094,"uid":34293,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:04:48.000Z","msg":"今天我決意要離開你<br />\n不管過去如何難忘記"},{"pid":"5821afe6f446f74c58936a5e9faa46b5e4c59e32","tid":601094,"uid":107157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:06:25.000Z","msg":"最撚憎垃圾假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8d2a490913250d7bc3390adac9a9b21503554d","tid":601094,"uid":125733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:07:20.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"9674f863e9a815c9f48e4a31347efd9d19a6a461","tid":601094,"uid":14719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5821afe6f446f74c58936a5e9faa46b5e4c59e32","tid":601094,"uid":107157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:06:25.000Z","msg":"最撚憎垃圾假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:12:22.000Z","msg":"係 決定離開連登 洗心革面 做個好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc597e639fcfb4db418552875db8fbf20ef2073","tid":601094,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:13:11.000Z","msg":"挽留"},{"pid":"7f888bc2e6327c5432356dc3abc77dfd93c3e555","tid":601094,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edf75798b7b15c1c918faa5a2d783b46e1632313","tid":601094,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:43:56.000Z","msg":"死五毛躝啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"765de62cbb875da783135abdacac127447876dbb","tid":601094,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9674f863e9a815c9f48e4a31347efd9d19a6a461","tid":601094,"uid":14719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5821afe6f446f74c58936a5e9faa46b5e4c59e32","tid":601094,"uid":107157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite